---
import { EDUCATION_TITLE, EDUCATION_DESCRIPTION } from "@/consts";
import Layout from "../layouts/WebPage.astro";
---

<Layout title={EDUCATION_TITLE} description={EDUCATION_DESCRIPTION}>
  <h1>Music Education: Mixing, Mastering & Cubase</h1>

  <p>Take your music production skills to the next level! I offer personalized education and resources for musicians, producers, and engineers who want to master the art of mixing, mastering, and using Steinberg Cubase.</p>

  <h2>Mixing & Mastering Education</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Fundamentals of EQ, compression, and effects</li>
    <li>Creative sound design and advanced processing</li>
    <li>Automation, workflow, and session organization</li>
    <li>Critical listening and reference techniques</li>
    <li>Mastering for streaming, CD, and vinyl</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Learn Steinberg Cubase</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Getting started: setup, audio/MIDI, and interface navigation</li>
    <li>Recording, editing, and arranging audio & MIDI</li>
    <li>Mixing in Cubase: channel strip, inserts, sends, and groups</li>
    <li>Using VST instruments and effects</li>
    <li>Exporting, project management, and workflow tips</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How I Teach</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>1-on-1 online lessons tailored to your goals</li>
    <li>Step-by-step video tutorials and written guides</li>
    <li>Project-based learning: work on your own music</li>
    <li>Feedback and Q&A for every lesson</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Get Started</h2>
  <p>Ready to learn? <a href="/contact/">Contact me</a> to book a lesson or ask about available resources!</p>

  <hr />

  <p><em>Have questions? Check out the <a href="/faq/">FAQ</a> or reach out directly.</em></p>
</Layout>
